Sam.

00:50:01.832 --> 00:50:04.877
I'm holding
her hand.

00:50:04.960 --> 00:50:07.087
He says he's
holding your hand.

00:50:17.139 --> 00:50:18.432
What are you doing?

00:50:18.724 --> 00:50:22.436
What do you think
you're doing to me?

00:50:22.561 --> 00:50:25.814
If you think I'm here for
my health, you're crazy.

00:50:25.981 --> 00:50:28.817
Sam's dead, OK?
He's dead.

00:50:28.943 --> 00:50:30.819
Tell her
I love her.

00:50:30.945 --> 00:50:32.863
He says
he loves you.

