00:51:34.675 --> 00:51:36.010
I don't know.

00:51:36.051 --> 00:51:37.511
Why is he
still here?

00:51:37.678 --> 00:51:39.555
He's stuck,
that's what it is.

00:51:39.680 --> 00:51:41.015
He's in between
worlds.

