Do you know what
that sounds like?

00:56:14.997 --> 00:56:17.332
You're talking ghosts here,
for Christ's sake.

00:56:19.126 --> 00:56:20.043
I'm sorry.

00:56:20.127 --> 00:56:22.921
This stuff just really
gets to me,

00:56:23.005 --> 00:56:23.922
you know?

00:56:24.006 --> 00:56:26.300
It's OK if you
don't believe me.

00:56:26.425 --> 00:56:27.926
I'm trying to, Molly.

00:56:31.513 --> 00:56:33.098
Look...

00:56:33.223 --> 00:56:36.143
if it'll make you
feel any better,

00:56:36.226 --> 00:56:40.355
I'll go check
this out, OK?

00:56:40.480 --> 00:56:43.358
I want you to try
and get some sleep.

00:56:43.483 --> 00:56:44.359
OK?

00:56:44.484 --> 00:56:46.320
All right.

00:56:47.487 --> 00:56:49.364
I'll call you
in the morning.

00:56:49.489 --> 00:56:50.365
OK.

00:57:18.393 --> 00:57:19.478
Be careful.

00:57:29.905 --> 00:57:31.782
[Knock Knock]

00:57:33.408 --> 00:57:34.326
Carl.

00:57:34.409 --> 00:57:37.329
What the hell
are you doing here?

00:57:38.622 --> 00:57:40.540
Who you been
talking to, Willy?

