A lot of women
know where I live.

00:57:55.055 --> 00:57:56.932
This is not a joke.

00:57:57.057 --> 00:57:58.975
She knows
about the murder.

00:57:59.101 --> 00:58:01.395
I want you
to find this bitch,

00:58:01.478 --> 00:58:02.979
whoever she is,

00:58:03.105 --> 00:58:04.981
and I want you to--

00:58:06.942 --> 00:58:09.236
Just get rid
of her, OK?

00:58:09.319 --> 00:58:13.824
I've got $4 million stuck
in a god damn computer.

